      "para_id": "Q004899.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Amar-Suena , whose name was proclaimed by Enlil in Nibru , the steadfast supporter of Enlil's temple , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , presented this ( seal ) to Šu-Kabta , his son-in-law ."
    }
  ],
